{"word":"G4388 - προτίθεμαι - protíthemai - prot-ith'-em-ahee - Purpose","slug":"G4388","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προτίθεμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>protíthemai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>prot-ith'-em-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Purpose"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - protithemai</b> - <i>prot-ith'-em-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>place before</i>, that is, (for oneself) to <i>exhibit</i>; (to oneself) to <i>propose</i> (<i>determine</i>): - purpose, set forth."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G114\">G114</a>, <a href=\"#/G115\">G115</a>, <a href=\"#/G1936\">G1936</a>, <a href=\"#/G2007\">G2007</a>, <a href=\"#/G3331\">G3331</a>, <a href=\"#/G3346\">G3346</a>, <a href=\"#/G3866\">G3866</a>, <a href=\"#/G3908\">G3908</a>, <a href=\"#/G4286\">G4286</a>, <a href=\"#/G4369\">G4369</a>, <a href=\"#/G5087\">G5087</a>"}]}